        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:16px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 360px;gap:16px;align-items:start">
          <div>
            <p style="color:var(--muted)">I’m a frontend developer who loves creating beautiful, accessible user interfaces and smooth user experiences. I focus on maintainable CSS architecture, performance, and accessibility. I enjoy mentoring juniors and learning about design systems.</p>

